LanguageData.CommandDeployWormholePortalB_PilotDesc: Deploy a wormhole to a target location to create a path spanning the two locations. A guide is needed to travel to unexplored areas.
LanguageData.WormholeNotLinked: This tunnel species has not yet deployed any wormholes
LanguageData.WormholeLinkLost: The tail of the wormhole deployed by this tunnel species was destroyed.
LanguageData.WormholePortalLinked: The deployment of tunnel species is completed! You can now quickly travel to the map of the tail of the tunnel species through its head.
LanguageData.WormholePortalB_Destroyed: The tail of the wormhole deployed by the tunnel species was destroyed
